{"TopicId":142895,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Add KSC marker to map","CreatedByName":"TheCardinal","CreatedById":22874,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T09:56:16Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"TheCardinal","CreatedById":22874,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T09:56:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne of the things i do is plant a flag at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E so i can guestimate when i should burn for reentry and land at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E. It would be very helpful for pilots if the location o the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E is visible in the map view.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"evileye.x","CreatedById":153755,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T11:37:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWaypoint Manager allows you to make custom waypoints. But also I use a flag at the end of runway as landing guidance system.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T12:13:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaha it\u0027s funny the really obvious things are easy to overlook. Totally agreed.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Champ","CreatedById":96425,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T12:41:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI strongly support this suggestion\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stoney3K","CreatedById":139954,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T14:30:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAgreed, why not have the flagpole as a targetable object by default?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BlkBltChemie","CreatedById":135033,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T16:24:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaha, just made a post on this \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/142431-ksc-map-view-icon-reprised/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Eabout a week ago\u003C/a\u003E now!\u00A0 Well you definitely have my vote; great minds and all!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-01T16:24:52Z\u0022 title=\u002207/01/2016 04:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 1, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by BlkBltChemie\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T16:29:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222657025\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142895\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467390266\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135033\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022BlkBltChemie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, BlkBltChemie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaha, just made a post on this \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/142431-ksc-map-view-icon-reprised/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Eabout a week ago\u003C/a\u003E now!\u00A0 Well you definitely have my vote; great minds and all!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re not the only one.\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnybody who has been a forum member as long as \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/22874-thecardinal/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002222874\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/22874-thecardinal/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@TheCardinal\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cs\u003Ecould\u003C/s\u003E should know this gets suggested fairly regularly. I am pretty sure SQUAD is aware of this request but SQUAD being SQUAD they refuse to act on it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DaMachinator","CreatedById":164681,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-01T17:24:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can see \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E from space, mostly because I know where it is... if you don\u0027t know where it is it\u0027s hard to find. Nonetheless I support this idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheCardinal","CreatedById":22874,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T07:33:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222657035\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142895\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467390582\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258254\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tex_NL\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 hours ago, Tex_NL said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re not the only one.\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnybody who has been a forum member as long as \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/22874-thecardinal/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002222874\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/22874-thecardinal/\u0022 rel=\u0022external\u0022\u003E@TheCardinal\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cs\u003Ecould\u003C/s\u003E should know this gets suggested fairly regularly. I am pretty sure SQUAD is aware of this request but SQUAD being SQUAD they refuse to act on it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps i could/should have known that. I didn\u0027t check the 327 pages of suggestions (sofar), i only checked the list of regular suggestions. Perhaps this should be add to that list.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DarkHawkGames","CreatedById":163651,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T09:05:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould it be hard to mod in? That might be an idea\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T17:51:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222658136\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142895\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467450328\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022163651\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DarkHawkGames\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, DarkHawkGames said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould it be hard to mod in? That might be an idea\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know that RemoteTech adds a red indicator dot to the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E to show that it\u0027s a signal endpoint.\u00A0 Have never looked at the source code, don\u0027t know how big a deal it was to code.\u00A0 I\u0027m guessing not very.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a feature I love, precisely because I too would really like to have a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E marker in the map view.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T17:57:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWouldn\u0027t it be easiest to mark the actual flag at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E as a \u0022flag\u0022 named \u0022Kerbal Space Center?\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean it\u0027s already a flag...why not just make it a \u0022flag?\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T19:26:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222658578\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142895\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467482279\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWouldn\u0027t it be easiest to mark the actual flag at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E as a \u0022flag\u0022 named \u0022Kerbal Space Center?\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean it\u0027s already a flag...why not just make it a \u0022flag?\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny kind of object category would suffice. Just as long as the runway and launchpad are targetable objects.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Megadeath","CreatedById":144236,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-03T01:43:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, pretty sure I\u0027m not the only person setting up flags at both ends of the runway! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stoney3K","CreatedById":139954,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-03T14:24:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222659091\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142895\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467510218\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022144236\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Megadeath\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Megadeath said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, pretty sure I\u0027m not the only person setting up flags at both ends of the runway! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich has the annoying side effect of always cycling through the flags if you switch vessels nearby. (Once again, anyone give ONE good reason to be able to switch to a flag as the active vessel?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-03T14:25:22Z\u0022 title=\u002207/03/2016 02:25  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 3, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Stoney3K\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bloojay","CreatedById":162865,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T13:44:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGive it to me know Squad.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T14:20:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI strongly agree. It would be very helpful.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-05T10:22:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222659586\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142895\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467555891\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022139954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stoney3K\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3.7.2016 at 4:24 PM, Stoney3K said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich has the annoying side effect of always cycling through the flags if you switch vessels nearby. (Once again, anyone give ONE good reason to be able to switch to a flag as the active vessel?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree, cycling should not include derbies of flags.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tyko","CreatedById":164179,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-06T18:45:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u002B1!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-07T17:38:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222659586\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142895\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467555891\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022139954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stoney3K\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 03/07/2016 at 3:24 PM, Stoney3K said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich has the annoying side effect of always cycling through the flags if you switch vessels nearby. (Once again, anyone give ONE good reason to be able to switch to a flag as the active vessel?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI use it to check on stuff between versions. \u00A0I planted flags near all the anomalies in one save and often open it up and activate the flag to look at the anomaly. \u00A0Yes I could have used a probe or \u00A0left a kerbal nearby, but I chose to have them mark the locations with a flag and come home for tea and biscuits.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}